'''Aban Ramḍan''' neɣ '''Ɛebban Ṛemḍan''' d argaz asarti aqbayli, i gelan d amenzawi deg umezruy n [[tagrawla Tadzayrit]] D netta i yellan d aqerru n tegrawla, d amsertay ugar n ukabar Tirni n Tleli Aɣelnaw [[FLN]].

== Tudert-is ==
 
Ilul Ɛebban Ṛemḍan ass n {{azmez|10|yunyu|1920}} deg [[Tamurt n Leqbayel|Tmurt n Leqbayel]]; taddart-is d [[Iɛezzuzen]] i d-yezgan tama n [[Larebɛa n At Yiraten]]. Baba-s qqaren-as Muḥend. Yemma-s qqaren-as Faṭima, tḥemmel-it aṭas acku yella d anelmad ifazen ger tezyiwin-is. Deg lawan-nni, ulac aṭas n yiɣerbazen imi tamurt n [[Dzayer]] tella ddaw [[tamḥarsa n Fransa|temḥarsa n Fransa]]. Ɛebban Ṛemḍan iṛuḥ ɣer [[Leblida]] akken ad ikemmel dinna leqraya-s deg teseddawit, ibbwi-d [[Lbbak]] (BAC) n [[tusnakt]] deg useggwas n [[1941]].


Deg tallit-nni i yebda yettfaq s yir tagnit i ttidiren Izzayriyen, ayen i t-yeğğan ad yeḥbes leqraya-s, ad imal ɣer tsertit. Ikcem s [[Amussu i Unalak n Tlelliyiin Timagdayin]] (MTLD, ''Mouvement Pour le Triomphe des Libertés Démocratiques''). Deg useggwas n [[1947]], yuɣal d imdebbeṛ deg ukabar-a, yerna yettikki deg [[tuddsa tuffirt]] (O.S., ''Organisation secrète'') i yella tettheggi ttṛad mgal [[Fransa]]. Adabu n Fransa ifaq yes-s, dɣa yeṭṭef aṭas n yimeɣnasen n umussu, yeḥkem-asen s lḥebs. Ɛebban Ṛemḍan yettwaṭṭef ula d netta, deg useggwas n [[1950]]. Yennuɣ deg lḥebs almi yuɣal yettuneḥsab d ameḥbus n tsertit, yesaa azref ad iɣer idlisen d yeɣmisen.


Yeffeɣ-ed deg [[yennayer 1955]]. Yerra ɣer taddart-is. Syin yeffeɣ s amadaɣ akken ad yeddu d yemdukal-is n tegrawla. Yuɣal iṛuḥ ɣer temdint n Lezzayer, yeṭṭef amkan n [[Rabaḥ Biṭaṭ|Biṭaṭ]] i yellan d ameḥbus. Seg [[meɣres 1955]] ar win n [[meɣres 1956|1956]], yessaweḍ Ɛebban ad yesdukel akk imussuten d yikabaren izzayriyen yellan niqal ur ttemsefhamen ara, akken ad ttekkin deg ttṛaḍ n uslelli aɣelnaw. Yumen d tadukli i yessawaḍen. D Abban Ṛemḍan i d-iheggan [[anejmaɛ n ṣṣumam]] anda i heggan lsas i tegrawla n Lezzayer.


Mlalen yergazen d tlawin n tegrawla deg [[Uzellagen]], deg [[Ɣuct 1956]]. 20 n wussan, nutni ttmeslayen ɣef liḥala n tmurt d umennuɣ n izzayriyen mgal amnekcam afṛansis. Dinna i d-ffɣent tektiwin sweyes ar a teddu tegrawla akwd tid iɣef ar a ters Lezzayer n uzekka.

Ɛebban Ṛemdan yemmut di laameṛ-is 37 iseggwasen, yettwanɣa di l'[[Merruk]] ass n {{azmez|27|dujamber|1957}}. Ɛebban Ṛemḍan d netta i d bab n tegrawla, d netta i yessawḍen ad yesbed lsas i tegrawla n Lezzayer maca xedɛent yemdukal-is akken xedɛen merra agdud akw d tmurt n Lezzayer.

